{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-excerpt-js","path":"/excerpts/nature_summer_flowers/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Flowers so colourful and bright,<br>\nIn their glory in the sun's light,<br>\nAt home amid the summer's heat,<br>\nGiving out a perfume so sweet,<br>\nThe summer flowers seem perfect,<br>\nIn near enough every aspect,<br>\nSo effortlessly they distract,<br>\nAs one's attention they attract,<br>\nCountless different kinds carve their mark,<br>\nThroughout every meadow and park,<br>\nThere for us to enjoy and pick,<br>\nWhile we waste our days and frolic,<br>\nAs gifts more poetic than speech,<br>\nWhen lovers and their loves meet,<br>\nOne of nature's finer artworks,<br>\nSaving scenes from seeming bleak.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 28, 2020","title":"Summer Flowers","audio":{"publicURL":"/static/49d082f5fc992cbd8149adee2a8131ca/Christian Lacdael - Nature - 28 Summer Flowers.mp3"},"icon":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/5cfe1b2670af1fba5ba93dbca1bd64f2/3c17d/poem%20summer%20flowers.png","srcSet":"/static/5cfe1b2670af1fba5ba93dbca1bd64f2/69585/poem%20summer%20flowers.png 200w,\n/static/5cfe1b2670af1fba5ba93dbca1bd64f2/497c6/poem%20summer%20flowers.png 400w,\n/static/5cfe1b2670af1fba5ba93dbca1bd64f2/3c17d/poem%20summer%20flowers.png 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/excerpts/nature_summer_flowers/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}